duck: quasi definition: having some resemblance usually by possession of certain attributes.
Quasi is  an American indie rock band formed in Portland, Oregon in 1993 by ex-husband and wife Sam Coomes (vocals, guitar, Rocksichord, various keyboards) and Janet Weiss (vocals and drums).
